name: Hotel-Management-MicroService-SpringBoot
description: A system built to achieve micro-service architecture. I have used industry level experience to build this scalable cluster of applications. Here, spring cloud, spring open feign, eureka server for service discovery and inter service communication is used. Deployable using K8 pods and forming network clusters. Rabin-carp rolling hash algo has been used for nginx load-balancing
